---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Trellix Security Solutions">

<main class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen">

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24">

<div class="flex items-center gap-6">

<img src="/logos/trellix.png" class="h-12" alt="Trellix">

<div>

<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400">
Trellix
</h1>

<p class="text-gray-300 mt-2">
Integrated platform for detection, response, and threat intelligence across endpoints and enterprise environments.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Core Products
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Trellix Endpoint Security</li>
<li>• Trellix EDR</li>
<li>• Trellix SIEM integrations</li>
<li>• Threat Intelligence Services</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Capabilities
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Advanced threat detection and analytics</li>
<li>• Centralized incident response workflows</li>
<li>• Endpoint telemetry and visibility</li>
<li>• Threat intelligence correlation</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Use Cases
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Enterprise endpoint protection</li>
<li>• SOC detection and response</li>
<li>• Threat hunting and investigations</li>
<li>• Incident orchestration and remediation</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Why Trellix
</h2>

<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
Trellix delivers an extensible detection and response platform that helps teams detect and remediate threats faster using integrated intelligence.
</p>

</div>

</section>

</main>

</Layout>
